  "subject": "Fix overlay template to support multiple networks",
  "commit_message": "Fix overlay template to support multiple networks\n\nExiting model doesn't allow multiple local networks to be associated\nwith a overlay inter-DC tunnel. Fix allows multiple networks to be\nassociated with a overlay tunnel, as well as multiple networks with\ndifferent overlay tunnel and corresponding configuration paramters.\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-443\n\nChange-Id: I3000da1cb99f8a2537c2535da7ebe97700623e45\nSigned-off-by: Arun S. Yerra <arun.yerra@huawei.com>\n",
